data.description: Indulge in convenient living at this stunning Ocean Lakes gem, minutes from Dam Neck and Oceana military bases, schools, and vibrant shopping and dining. Revel in the fresh ambiance of newly painted walls, plush carpets, and a contemporary kitchen featuring quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and immaculate hardwood floors downstairs. Step into a backyard oasis surrounded by a brand-new fence, perfect for outdoor retreats. The renovated bathrooms boast laminate flooring and state-of-the-art shower heads. Delight in community luxuries like pools, playgrounds, tennis courts, and a fitness room. This home harmonizes elegance with convenience—seize your chance to own in this highly desirable location!
